Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:19.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, you don't look like you've\Nopened up your mind yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:22.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get swept up by\NGamatatsu's movements!
