Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,arrange things your way,\Nthen just express yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:29.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:30.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:36.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
