Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:08.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that cloud...\Nlooks like a cream puff...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks yummy!
