Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:20.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did you feel something\Njust now, Gamatatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:22.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me this?
