Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:37.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go!\N- Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go! Go! Go!\N- Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:44.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's your name?\N- Gamatatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't mean\Nyou're on the same wavelength.
